      bypass_other_policies                 = false
      server_certificates                   = "ALLOW"
      ocsp_check                            = true
      block_ssl_traffic_with_no_sni_enabled = true
      min_tls_version                       = "SERVER_TLS_1_0"
    }
  }
  groups {
        id = [ data.zia_group_management.this.id ]
    }
}
```

### Action - DO_NOT_DECRYPT - Bypass Rule (True)

```hcl

